HIV pixel clustering - normalize by norm of vector (sqrt(sum(x^2)))

Candace Liu

July 14, 2020

  • Gaussian blur sigma=2, no arcsinh, k=20
  • z-score cap=3 for hierarchical clustering, iterative z-score threshold=3
  • For each pixel, divide each marker by norm (square root of sum of each marker squared)
  • No iterations (all z-scores under 3)

No z-score cap for hierarchical clusters

Z-score cap=3 for hierarchical clusters
